summary: It’s time for my 2018 cosplay year-in-review. This year, I did 3 new cosplays (Disgust, Lich!Barry, and Washimi), 2 LARP...
caption:
It’s time for my 2018 cosplay year-in-review. This year, I did 3 new cosplays (Disgust, Lich!Barry, and Washimi), 2 LARP costumes (superhero and pirate), 2 party costumes (Miss Scarlett for NYE and A Salt & Battery for Halloween), and helped sew cosplays for 2 friends (Taako and Lup).
•
•
I’m thankful for all the friends who I get to do this hobby with; you inspire me and make it fun. Let’s see what we do in 2019!
•
•
📷 credit: @journeysincolor for Disgust and The Adventure Zone photos; La Vie En Photos for Washimi
•
